<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.ishidawg.LeShade</id>
  
  <name>LeShade</name>
  <summary>A ReShade manager for linux. </summary>
  
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      LeShade is a ReShade manager for linux, like a mod manager but for reshade. It's intended to be used with Wine and Proton applications.
    </p>
    <p>It's features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Direct3D 8.x support<li>
      <li>ReShade with addon and non-addon support<li>
      <li>ReShade with a specific release version support<li>
      <li>Uninstall ReShade from previous installations<li>
      <li>Many repositories<li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
